This album is conducted throughout the mid nineties, a period in my life where I had a bit of a midlife crisis. My husband had just left me, two of my eight cats died due to food poisoning and my favorite teddy bear got lost in the woods. This song reminds me of my husband, which isn't good, because he was an awful man I only married due to his money.
